  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4869969/" class="title-link">本来可以给四星的。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4869969"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/airixz/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2835937-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/airixz/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">不言自语</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-03-21"
      class="main-meta">2011-03-21 22:55:23</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4869969_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书的内容和观点都很好，值四星甚至更高。不过作者的文风实在受不了。简简单单一个观点，一句话就可以说明白，作者非得把每个词都加上“就像某某说的.....&#34;，东引西引得，弄出巨长无比、没有标点的句子，以示其博览群书么？读着累死了，以后再也不看这个作者的书了。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
